# Day 11 – AI File Summarizer 🤖

## What it does
Reads any text file, sends the content to Groq's
LLM API, and saves a clean AI-generated summary
(3 bullet points + one main takeaway) to a new file.

## Tech Stack
- Python 3
- groq
- python-dotenv

## Setup
pip install groq python-dotenv

# Create a .env file:
GROQ_API_KEY=your_key_here

## How to run
python summarizer.py

# When prompted:
Enter the filename to summarise: notes.txt

## What I learned
- Groq API client setup and authentication
- System prompts to control AI behaviour
- Combining file I/O with live AI API calls
- Saving AI output directly to a new file

## Output
Creates summary_[filename] with an AI-generated
summary of the input file.
